latestIgtvVideos.title: Night skincare routine
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Products used 
cleanser : @simpleskincareindia facewash
[ i was using @biotique_world neem facewash for 4years , just now switched to simple brand]

serum : @beminimalist__ tranexamix acid serum for acne scars 
if you have sensitive skin like mine , please dont go for this , either choose their alpha arbutin , its their best serum.

Moisturiser : @neutriderm_india vitamin e moisturiser
the day i use tranexamic acid i choose to stay away from actives so this is the best option to pair with.

thats it no more product just a lip balm :) 💋 from @laneigeindia
